# Indoor walkable — cci checkpoint (pre-lb*)

When rebaking or tuning **cci*** indoor clusters:

1. Read `Tools/indoor_walkable_checkpoint_cci.json`.
2. Golden: `D:/1/2026-7-18_21-57-38_indoor-cci-pre-lb`.
3. Auto bulk routes `cci*` → `--pre-lb-walkable` (slope-up only). Do **not** apply lb* shell/weld/strips.
4. Membership keys: float64 SOURCE_BASIS before Vector3.
5. Bulk preview: `export_all_indoor_clusters.ps1 -LabelPrefix cci -SkipManifestRebuild`.
6. Production nav: `-WriteNavRes -SkipPreviewGlb` → `GeneratedIndoorNavMeshes/` (also run via `TerrainNavigationBaker` when `BakeIndoorNav`).
